又變嘿咻嘿咻。男欲內發，女言不可，搖頭嗔目，元陽閉穴。」此之謂也。"},{"pid":"addef46a17d93ea2f1536062039d6437c8e63338","tid":689215,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f89ee2ec93ee303bf1b45dc36e516db1bd3dc1","tid":689215,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"揾唔到套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa29d8f95608c0654a57840e732b0dc847f4dd3d","tid":689215,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"新聞寫到好似甜故咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca564c192feddf386f0eb757756b8b64747cc2ba","tid":689215,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa29d8f95608c0654a57840e732b0dc847f4dd3d","tid":689215,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"新聞寫到好似甜故咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"台灣報紙特色嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}